{
  "$jason": {
    "head": {
      "title": "Render dynamic main page",
      "actions": {
        "$load": {
          "type": "$render"
        }
      },
      "templates": {
        "body": {
          "style": {
            "background": "{{$global.background}}",
            "color": "{{$global.fontColor}}",
            "border": "none",
            "align": "center"
          },
          "header": {
            "title": "Accueil",
            "style": {
              "font": "Roboto",
              "size": 25,
              "background": "#2d3436",
              "color": "white"
            },
            "menu": {
              "image": "file://images/logout.png",
              "style": {
                "color": "white"
              },
              "action": {
                "type": "$back"
              }
            },
            "leftButton": {
              "text": "☰",
              "style": {
                "size": 45,
                "width": 20,
                "minWidth": 90,
                "color": "white",
                "background": "#2d3436"
              },
              "action": {
                "type": "$util.picker",
                "options": {
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "text": "Acceuil",
                      "action": {
                        "type": "$href",
                        "options": {
                          "url": "file://ui/home.json",
                          "transition": "push",
                          "animation": "pushleft",
                          "view": "jason"
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Actualités",
                      "action": {
                        "type": "$href",
                        "options": {
                          "url": "file://ui/news.json",
                          "transition": "push",
                          "animation": "pushleft",
                          "view": "jason"
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Nos annonces",
                      "action": {
                        "type": "$href",
                        "options": {
                          "url": "file://ui/announcements.json",
                          "transition": "push",
                          "animation": "pushleft",
                          "view": "jason"
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Vidéo",
                      "action": {
                        "type": "$href",
                        "options": {
                          "url": "file://ui/video.json",
                          "transition": "push",
                          "animation": "pushleft",
                          "view": "jason"
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Scan code a barre",
                      "action": {
                        "type": "$href",
                        "options": {
                          "url": "file://ui/qrcode.json",
                          "transition": "modal",
                          "view": "jason"
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "paramètrages",
                      "action": {
                        "type": "$href",
                        "options": {
                          "url": "file://ui/about.json",
                          "transition": "push",
                          "animation": "pushleft",
                          "view": "jason"
                        }
                      }
                    }

                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "sections": [
            {
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "label",
                  "text": "Moto Magazine - Le Pavé dans la mare est un mensuel français destiné à suivre l'actualité motocycliste, notamment dans le domaine de la sécurité routière, de la pratique quotidienne et passionnelle de la moto et dans le domaine sportif. La rédaction teste des motos du marché, le plus souvent sous forme d'essais comparatifs ou de bilans occasions et fiabilités. Divers tests de matériels pour le motard (casques, vestes, chaussure, etc.) et sa moto (pneus, bagagerie, consommables, GPS, etc.) sont également réalisés.",
                  "style": {
                    "font": "Roboto",
                    "size": 16,
                    "color": "{{$global.fontColor}}",
                    "padding": 10
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "image",
                  "url": "file://images/art1.jpg",
                  "style": {
                    "width": "100%",
                    "align": "center"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "label",
                  "text": "La revue est créée en 1983 par les Éditions de la FFMC2 sous le titre « Le Pavé dans la mare ». Elle est réalisée par une équipe mixte de professionnels et d’essayeurs bénévoles1 et des militants de la Fédération française des motards en colère (FFMC). Elle devient « Moto Magazine » dans les années 1990. L'entreprise publie Moto Magazine qui est le titre moto le plus diffusé de France3,4 et des hors-séries.",
                  "style": {
                    "font": "Roboto",
                    "size": 16,
                    "color": "{{$global.fontColor}}",
                    "padding": 10
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "image",
                  "url": "file://images/art2.jpg",
                  "style": {
                    "width": "70%",
                    "align": "center"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "label",
                  "text": "Une version numérique existe depuis janvier 2013, comprenant des articles avec support vidéo et plusieurs milliers de petites annonces.",
                  "style": {
                    "font": "Roboto",
                    "size": 16,
                    "color": "{{$global.fontColor}}",
                    "padding": 10
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "layers": [
            {
              "type": "button",
              "url": "file://images/qrcode.png",
              "style": {
                "animation": {
                  "type": "{{$global.animation}}"
                },
                "width": 40,
                "box-shadow": "10px 10px 5px #888888",
                "height": 40,
                "right": 20,
                "bottom": 190,
                "background": "#8e44ad",
                "color": "#ffffff",
                "font": "Roboto",
                "size": 30,
                "corner_radius": 75
              },
              "action": {
                "type": "$global.set",
                "options": {
                  "animation": "hide"
                },
                "success": {
                  "type": "$render",
                  "success": {
                    "type": "$href",
                    "options": {
                      "url": "file://ui/qrcode.json",
                      "transition": "modal",
                      "view": "jason"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "button",
              "url": "file://images/video.png",
              "style": {
                "animation": {
                  "type": "{{$global.animation}}"
                },
                "width": 40,
                "box-shadow": "10px 10px 5px #888888",
                "height": 40,
                "right": 20,
                "bottom": 140,
                "background": "#27ae60",
                "color": "#ffffff",
                "font": "Roboto",
                "size": 30,
                "corner_radius": 75
              },
              "action": {
                "type": "$global.set",
                "options": {
                  "animation": "hide"
                },
                "success": {
                  "type": "$render",
                  "success": {
                    "type": "$href",
                    "options": {
                      "url": "file://ui/video.json",
                      "transition": "push",
                      "animation": "pushleft",
                      "view": "jason"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "button",
              "url": "file://images/about.png",
              "style": {
                "animation": {
                  "type": "{{$global.animation}}"
                },
                "width": 40,
                "box-shadow": "10px 10px 5px #888888",
                "height": 40,
                "right": 20,
                "bottom": 90,
                "background": "#c0392b",
                "color": "#ffffff",
                "font": "Roboto",
                "size": 30,
                "corner_radius": 75
              },
              "action": {
                "type": "$global.set",
                "options": {
                  "animation": "hide"
                },
                "success": {
                  "type": "$render",
                  "success": {
                    "type": "$href",
                    "options": {
                      "url": "file://ui/about.json",
                      "transition": "push",
                      "animation": "pushleft",
                      "view": "jason"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "button",
              "url": "file://images/plus.png",
              "style": {
                "width": 60,
                "box-shadow": "10px 10px 5px #888888",
                "height": 60,
                "right": 20,
                "bottom": 20,
                "background": "#2980b9",
                "color": "#ffffff",
                "font": "Roboto",
                "size": 30,
                "corner_radius": 75
              },
              "action": {
                "type": "$global.set",
                "options": {
                  "animation": "show"
                },
                "success": {
                  "type": "$render"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

